Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.testng.integration.properties

Enum RefreshEachTimeBefore

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RefreshEachTimeBefore>
      • ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.testng.integration.properties.RefreshEachTimeBefore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<java.lang.Class<? extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>>

    public enum RefreshEachTimeBefore
extends java.lang.Enum<RefreshEachTimeBefore>
implements java.util.function.Supplier<java.lang.Class<? extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation>>
    This enum is designed to define the strategy of the invoking of Refreshable.refresh() by engines of TestNg. It is supposed to be invoked before methods annotated by BeforeSuite and/or BeforeTest and/or BeforeClass and/or BeforeGroups and/or BeforeMethod and/or Test.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      ALL_TEST_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first annotated by BeforeTest is run.
      BEFORE_METHOD_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first method annotated by BeforeMethod is run before any test.
      CLASS_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first BeforeClass - method of a class is run.
      GROUP_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first BeforeGroups - method of a group is run.
      METHOD_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before any method annotated by Test is run.
      SUITE_STARTING
      This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first method annotated by BeforeSuite is run.

      • SUITE_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore SUITE_STARTING

      • ALL_TEST_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore ALL_TEST_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first annotated by BeforeTest is run.

        Rule:

        Refreshable.refresh() is invoked when:

        1. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before any not static BeforeSuite/BeforeTest-method.

      • CLASS_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore CLASS_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first BeforeClass - method of a class is run.

        Rule:

        Refreshable.refresh() is invoked when:

        1. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeSuite/BeforeTest/BeforeClass-method and any Test-method has not been started still.

        2. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeClass-method and any Test-method has not been started still.

      • GROUP_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore GROUP_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first BeforeGroups - method of a group is run.

      • BEFORE_METHOD_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore BEFORE_METHOD_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before the first method annotated by BeforeMethod is run before any test.

        Rule:

        Refreshable.refresh() is invoked when:

        1. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeSuite/BeforeTest/BeforeClass/BeforeGroups/ BeforeMethod-method and any Test-method has not been started still.

        2. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeMethod-method and any Test-method has not been started still.

      • METHOD_STARTING

        public static final RefreshEachTimeBefore METHOD_STARTING
        This element is used to define the strategy to invoke the Refreshable.refresh() each time before any method annotated by Test is run.

        Rule:

        Refreshable.refresh() is invoked when:

        1. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeSuite/BeforeTest/BeforeClass/BeforeGroups/ BeforeMethod-method and any Test-method has not been started still.

        2. Refreshable.refresh() has not been invoked before some not static BeforeMethod-method and any Test-method has not been started still.
